I *love* the cartoony fantasy style graphics of WoW. Not only do they look top notch, they will also perform a hell of alot better on a wide variety of systems, as opposed to Sony's methodology of &quot;Hey, lets cram too many polys into models so that nobody can comfortably play the game on any system with over 20 models on screen&quot;. Ever been to PoP zones with luclin models on and medium or better detail settings? How about Crypt of Nadox?(Which btw you still get the crappy poly intensive luclin models regardless of what's in your options)<br>
<br>
I understand that some people may not prefer the cartoony graphic style that WoW is offering. But WoW will bend EQ over a table and give it a hard fuck in the ass, that's all there is to it.<br>
<br>
